/>\r\n<br />\r\nSelect <strong>download quality</strong> for quality changes as required<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src="http://download.file/uploads/articles/ytd-select-quality.jpg" alt="Ytd video downloader - select quality" width="600" height="455" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\nChange the archive folder by clicking the folder icon next to the “<strong>Save to</strong>”<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src="http://download.file/uploads/articles/ytd-downloading.jpg" alt="Ytd video downloader - start download video" width="600" height="458" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou should note that auto-convert feature video files only in the Pro version of <strong>YTD Video Downloader</strong>. If you want to convert with normal demand, we select the Convert tab, select the original video Select the video from the file, select the file format (Convert video to), corresponding quality (Conversion quality), directory reserve (Save to) ... and click Convert Video to start.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src="http://download.file/uploads/articles/ytd-convert-video.jpg" alt="Ytd video convert" width="600" height="456" /><br type="_moz" />', 0, 1, 0, 20, 4, 1, '2015-10-01 09:32:41', '2017-03-29 22:27:05'),
(5, 'Free download manager ', 'free-download-manager', 'Free Download Manager', 'http://www.freedownloadmanager.org/', 'Free download manager, Download free download manager, Free download manager download', 'Free download manager is a 100% software with the function of increasing download speeds and support to download music, games, documents..easily and quickly', 846, 2, 2, 'http://f0.freedownloadmanager.org/fdminst.exe', '', '', '', '3.9.6 build 1614', '10.2', 'Windows 9x/ME/2000/2003/XP/Vista/7/8', '', 'free-download-manager-icon.jpg', 'free-download-manager.jpg', 'Tăng tốc tải xuống và hỗ trợ tải xuống', 'Free download manager is a 100% software with the function of increasing download speeds and support to download music, games, documents..easily and quickly', 'When you need to download videos, documents or even email from a website or serve , your task can not be accepted because of a <strong>larger file</strong>( file size is restricted). This is very depressing and need a quick and easy solution. What you need is a freeware that helps you to solve the problem by splitting the file into bite sized pieces for you to increase download speeds. That’s when you need <strong>Free download Manager</strong>.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src="http://freefile.vn/uploaded/free-download-manager-intro.jpg" alt="Screenshot of Free download Manager for Windows" width="600" height="379" /><br />\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: ''Times New Roman'', serif;">Screenshot of </span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:&#10;115%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;">Free download Manager for Windows<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '<strong>Free Download Manager</strong> – a powerful management for fast file download. The software allows to download all kinds of files with high-speed of downloading. FDM accelerates downloads by splitting the files into pieces &#160;and then downloads them simultaneously. Therefore, the download speed will be increased to 600% or even more. The software also can continue downloading even when the download fails, and the internet users don’t have to download again from the beginning after a certain error.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Newly updated function in version 3.9.6 build 1614</strong><br />\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Support Firefox above 40</li>\r\n    <li>Supervise video flash: Support Internet Explorer 11</li>\r\n    <li>Support Internet Explorer 11 may be crashed by add-on FDM</li>\r\n    <li>Support Unicode</li>\r\n    <li>Repair troubleshooting errors which is displayed icon in the tray of system.</li>\r\n    <li>Download Youtube through the process</li>\r\n    <li>Fix general bug</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<br />\r\nSupport HTTP / FTP / BitTorrent: FDM enables users to download files and the whole websites from any serves via HTTP, HTTPS and FTP. Users also can <strong>download files</strong> by protocol BitTorrent.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Advanced function of Free Download Manager</strong><br />\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Download RTSP / MMS.</li>\r\n    <li>FDM saves the list of data downloads and other services as necessary.</li>\r\n    <li>Automatically update Firefox extension.</li>\r\n    <li>Support the option of decrease traffic usage on browser activity for Firefox.</li>\r\n    <li>Compatibility issues with Internet Explorer 10.</li>\r\n    <li>Fixes errors.</li>\r\n</ul>', '<strong>Free Download Manager</strong> is a tool to increase download speeds by up to 5 times, resume and schedule downloads. Comprehensive error recovery and resume capability will restart broken or interrupted downloads due to lost connections, network problems, computer shutdowns, or unexpected power outages. Simple graphic user interface makes IDM user friendly and easy to use.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Free Internet Download Manager</strong> has a smart download logic accelerator that features intelligent dynamic file segmentation and safe multipart downloading technology to accelerate your downloads. Moreover, the freeware segments downloaded files dynamically during download process and reuses available connections without additional connect and login stages to achieve best acceleration performance.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSimultaneously, the users can <strong>easily download</strong> &#160;not only files from many other mirror and any important part of a zip file.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div>Free download manager is a multilingual tool that is translated into 30 languages.<br />\r\n&#160;</div>\r\n<div>When the download is stopped, users do not need to start from the beginning again. <strong>Free Download Manager</strong> can resume the download process when the error occurred. This saves you time, money and effort.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIncluding the above functions, with the program, you can easily order the files in classification, transforming them into available folders. A smart schedule allows you to start and stop the downloads, as well as perform other actions (running applications, establish or hang connectors, ...) at the same time.</div>', 0, 1, 0, 20, 4, 1, '2015-10-15 10:54:22', '2017-03-29 22:27:24');

